<item>
            <title>[LU-9127] too many debug messages from tgt_cb_last_committed()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9127</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;tgt_cb_last_committed() prints a D_HA message even if last_committed was not updated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is the cpu overhead associated with a bunch of similar (and mostly useless) messages and potential Lustre debug log overflow.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A trivial patch will be uploaded shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
